SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v6.fare_id||'"', '"'||v7.fare_basis_code||'"',
 '"'||v8.booking_class||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, flight_fare v5, fare v6,
 fare_basis v7, class_of_service v8 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MIAMI'))) AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) 
AND ((v5.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) AND ((v6.fare_basis_code = ANY v7.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v7.booking_class = ANY v8.booking_class) 
AND NOT (v8.booking_class IS NULL)))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NEW YORK ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MIAMI ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FARE . FARE_ID FROM FARE WHERE FARE . FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS . FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS . BOOKING_CLASS IN ( SELECT CLASS_OF_SERVICE . BOOKING_CLASS FROM CLASS_OF_SERVICE WHERE NOT ( CLASS_OF_SERVICE.BOOKING_CLASS IS NULL ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
